vg> Supports the body's own melatonin\n  pathways</div>                                                                                       \n            <div class=\"ariya-product__benefit ariya-reveal ariya-delay-4\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" \n  viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0\n  1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><path d=\"M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3\"/></svg> Reduces nighttime stress and tension</div>     \n            <div class=\"ariya-product__benefit ariya-reveal ariya-delay-5\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\"\n  viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 \n  1 1-5.93-9.14\"/><path d=\"M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3\"/></svg> No artificial colors or preservatives</div>\n          </div>                                                                                       \n                                                                                                       \n          <div class=\"ariya-product__price\">{{ product.price | money | default: '$44.99' }}</div>\n          <p class=\"ariya-product__price-sub\">60 capsules &bull; 30 servings</p>                       \n                                              \n          <div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">                                          \n            <a href=\"{{ product.url | default: '/products/calm-nights' }}\" class=\"ariya-btn\n  ariya-btn--primary\">View Full Details</a>                                                            \n            <form method=\"post\" action=\"/cart/add\" style=\"display:inline;\">                            \n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"id\" value=\"{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id  \n  }}\">                                                                                                 \n              <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"quantity\" value=\"1\">\n              <button class=\"ariya-btn ariya-btn--secondary\" type=\"submit\">Add to Cart</button>        \n            </form>                                                                                    \n          </div>                              \n        </div>                                                                                         \n                  \n      </div>                                                                                           \n    </div>\n  </div>",
