    "team_section": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ariya-section ariya-team\">  \n    <div class=\"ariya-container\">\n      <div class=\"ariya-team__header ariya-reveal\">                                                    \n        <p class=\"ariya-label\">The Team</p>   \n        <div class=\"ariya-divider ariya-divider--center\"></div>                                        \n        <h2 class=\"ariya-heading ariya-heading--lg\">Built by people who needed better.</h2>\n      </div>                                                                                           \n                                          \n      <div class=\"ariya-team__cards\">                                                                  \n                                                                                                       \n        <div class=\"ariya-team__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-1\">\n          <img class=\"ariya-team__card-image\"                                                          \n  src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0989/3734/0186/files/IMG_6155.jpg?v=1776108248\" alt=\"Aria\n  Ghadimi\" style=\"width:100%;object-fit:cover;\">                                                       \n          <h3>Aria Ghadimi</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-team__card-role\">Founder &amp; CEO | Certified Nutrition Coach</span>     \n          <p>Aria grew up playing football and running track — disciplined, clean eating, fully\n  committed to his health. But despite doing everything right, he struggled with poor sleep, chronic   \n  fatigue, and acne nobody could explain. That search for answers led him to nutrition coaching — and  \n  exposed how broken the supplement industry really was. He built Ariya because the brand he needed    \n  didn't exist.</p>                                                                                    \n        </div>                                                                                         \n                                                                                                       \n        <div class=\"ariya-team__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-2\">\n          <img class=\"ariya-team__card-image\"\n  src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0989/3734/0186/files/IMG_6153.jpg?v=1776108256\" alt=\"Arian\n  Ghadimi\" style=\"width:100%;object-fit:cover;\">\n          <h3>Arian Ghadimi</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-team__card-role\">Co-Founder &amp; Head of Operations</span>               \n          <p>Arian grew up playing competitive soccer and developed an early habit of questioning what\n  was actually in the products he used. Long before Ariya existed, he was reading labels, cutting out  \n  unnecessary ingredients, and pushing his family toward a cleaner way of living. When Ariya came\n  together, it was a natural step for him to help build what he had already been living.</p>           \n        </div>                                                                                         \n                                                                                                       \n        <div class=\"ariya-team__card ariya-reveal ariya-delay-3\">                                      \n          <img class=\"ariya-team__card-image\"\n  src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0989/3734/0186/files/IMG_6154.jpg?v=1776108253\" alt=\"Owen\n  Pastore\" style=\"width:100%;object-fit:cover;\">\n          <h3>Owen Pastore</h3>\n          <span class=\"ariya-team__card-role\">Co-Founder &amp; Head of Formulation | CPT, Nutrition    \n  Coach &amp; CES</span>                      \n          <p>Owen has over four years of coaching experience, working with everyday clients to         \n  competitive athletes. The more he coached, the harder it became to recommend supplements he actually\n  trusted. That frustration is why he helped build Ariya.</p>                                          \n        </div>\n                                                                                                       \n      </div>      \n    </div>                                                                                             \n  </div>",
